
PREREQUSITES
------------
PHP 4.x
MySQL 4.x


INSTALLTION
-----------

1) Copy the acl directory to where mambo is installed (e.g. /var/www/mambo)

2) Edit acl/inc_acl

   #-- database config --
   $host = "localhost";
   $dbuser="dbuser"; $dbpassword="dbpassword";

4) Copy the sample mod_statistics.php to the mambo's module directory overwriting the exicing file (e.g. /var/www/mambo/modules). To test it you should first install the graph module.


